      <title>埃塞俄比亚计划允许外国银行收购本地银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ethiopia-plans-to-allow-foreign-banks-to-acquire-local-lenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚部长理事会批准了一项法案，为海外银行收购国内银行的股份铺平了道路，标志着三十年来禁止外国人进入该行业的政策的结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ethiopia-plans-to-allow-foreign-banks-to-acquire-local-lenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
